we can use a crd called ClusterAnalysisTemplate if we want to share the same template across multiple namespaces
we just need to change the kind from AnalysisTemplate to ClusterAnalysisTemplate
and in the rollout :
if its pre promotion add this :
      prePromotionAnalysis:    #### cluster-pre-Promotion Analysis
        templates:
        - templateName: <templateName>
          clusterScope: true
if its post promotion add this :
      postPromotionAnalysis:    #### cluster-post-Promotion Analysis
        templates:
        - templateName: <templateName>
          clusterScope: true
all other parameters stays the same for the template and the rollout